{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["Sirius' Improvement Plan\n\n<size=45>Chapter 3 - The Maids' Aid<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"To be able to blend in among the crowd at the banquet, there is a need for Sirius to understand precisely what a maid's duties are and how a maid should behave.","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"effects":[{"delay":2,"active":true,"name":"memoryFog"}],"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":202120},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"In addition, now that Sirius have been selected for the assignment, there is a need to improve on her ability to serve as a secretary.","actor":202120,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"...Is this an accurate summary of your request, Master?","actor":202120,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"I went to the Royal Navy Maids and requested their guidance on Sirius.","dir":1,"effects":[{"active":false,"name":"memoryFog"}],"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I humbly request your gentle treatment, Belfast.","actor":202200,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Although ordinary maid business has never been Sirius' job, this is a special case.","actor":202120,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"For this instance, don't worry about the tasks you are usually assigned; let's all take turns explaining.","actor":202120,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Very well. If it's for my Master's sake, I'll do anything...!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":202200},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"First, we will have to teach you proper etiquette.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":202220},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Well, I say there's no need to be overly formal, so let's instead start by teaching her the dos and don'ts, shall we?","actor":202210,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"When cleaning the Commander's office, you should start with cleaning the shelves, not sweep the floor, as it is easier that way.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":202080},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I see. That will come handy in the future.","actor":202200,"subActors":[{"actor":202180,"pos":{"x":1125}}],"actorName":"Belette & Sirius","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Emm, I don't think there's anything special that Contestant Kent can teach you.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":203030},{"expression":7,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Maybe I could teach you how to skip work without Belfast finding out about it?","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":203040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"...I would be quite interested in knowing how you do so.","actor":202120,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"......","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"...I feel I have become aware of just how much I don't know...","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":202200},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Looks like Sirius is getting closer to becoming a made maid.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"TIANLANGXING3","fadeOut":1.5}